extends ../../layouts/layout-beta.pug

block content
  #content.section--primary
    .container
      h1 Thank you for your petition
        span.sr-only.
        span Object to Additional Provision 2 of the High Speed Rail (West Midlands to Crewe) Bill

      br
      .status--highlight
        p.lead The information on this page will be sent to 
          i 'petitioner-email-address@domain.com'
          |  in the next 15 minutes.

  section
    .container
      h2 What happens next

      ul.track--alternative
        li
          h3.typography--light We'll email you within 14 days about how to pay the &pound;20 admin fee, unless you paid it when objecting to the original bill
        li
          h3.typography--light We'll publish your petition on our website. This will include your name and address.
        li
          h3.typography--light Weâ€™ll send your petition to HS2 Ltd, who may contact you to discuss it.
        li
          h3.typography--light We'll also send your petition to the Department for Transport (DfT). They can challenge it if they don't believe you are affected by additional provision one.
        li
          h3.typography--light You will usually be invited to give evidence to the committee about your petition. Hearings are scheduled for spring/summer 2019.

  section
    .container
      h2 Withdrawing your petition

      p You can withdraw your petition by emailing us at #[+link('mailto:prbohoc@parliament.uk', 'prbohoc@parliament.uk')].

      p Anyone named on a petition can withdraw from the petition, leaving the remaining petitioners to continue with it.

      p Withdrawn petitions will not be removed from the website.

  section
    .container
      h2 Changing contact information

      p If you want to change the main contact for your petition call us on #[+link('tel:02072193250', '020 7219 3250')].

  section
    .container
      h2 Give feedback
      p Help us improve this petitioning process by completing our 
        +link('#', 'feedback form')(target='_blank')
          span.sr-only (This link will open in a new window)
        | .

  section
    .container
      h2 Bill updates
      p For news and updates on the Bill, visit the  
        +link('http://www.parliament.uk/business/committees/committees-a-z/commons-select/high-speed-rail-west-midlands-crewe-bill-select-committee-commons', 'High Speed Rail (West Midlands to Crewe) Bill Committee website')(target='_blank')
          span.sr-only (This link will open in a new window)
        | .
